tics Act, 1940 (23 of 1940), the Central Government hereby prohibits the manufacture and sale of parenteral preparations containing fixed dose combination of streptomycin with penicillins with effect from 1st January, 1998. [No. X-l 1014/5/96-DMS & PFA] RENU SAHNI DHAR, Jt. Secy. Printed by the Manager. Govt of India Press, Ring Road, Mayapuri, New Delhi-110064 and Published by the Controller of Publications, Delhi-110054 — 1997. -- 2 of 2 --",
